The '''Whitesun family''' was a family that lived on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. For three generations as of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] they had been moisture farmers and were known as the best of them in the area around [[Mos Eisley/Legends|Mos Eisley]].

The Whitesun family bloodline included the siblings [[Beru Whitesun Lars/Legends|Beru]], [[Dama Whitesun Brunk|Dama]], [[Haro Whitesun|Haro]], and perhaps [[Coolie]].

When [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] became Darth Vader, his son, [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]], was cared for by Beru and her husband, [[Owen Lars/Legends|Owen Lars]]. Owen and Beru, whom Luke called "Uncle Owen" and "Aunt Beru," were killed by [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtroopers]] in [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]].

